sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Activity Details Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant FS as Storage
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open activity details
    UI->>LW: mount(id)
    LW->>DB: Find activity by id
    DB-->>LW: Activity record
    LW-->>UI: Render tabs and metadata

    User->>UI: View attachment
    UI->>LW: getAttachmentUrl()
    LW->>FS: Check public file exists
    alt File exists
        FS-->>LW: Exists + URL
        LW-->>UI: Render attachment link
    else Missing file
        FS-->>LW: Not found
        LW-->>UI: Hide/disable attachment link
    end

    User->>UI: Change language/tab
    UI->>LW: changeLanguage(lang) / tab switch
    LW-->>UI: Re-render localized content
